text: Gumerovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Duvan-Mechetlinsky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 166 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye, 3 km from Duvan-Mechetlino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Gumerovo, Mechetlinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
